t comes with a 3oz bag of paydirt (total weight) and each pay dirt bag contains fine gold flour and coarse gold flakes in the 20-30 mesh size range; Sealed in premium resealable bag</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"><br></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">PROSPECTING GOLD PANNING EQUIPMENT - This 10 piece gold panning kit is a great beginner kit that includes tools designed to help you identify, clean, and collect valuable gold flakes and minerals from your pay dirt out in the field. Everything you'll need to get started on your gold prospecting adventure</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">PAY DIRT PROSPECTORS SCOOP – This small hand trowel scooper is an essential mining tool for your arsenal of gold prospecting and metal detecting equipment, you can count on it to dig through dirt, sand, and silt in any weather.  It’s made of durable, high-quality ABS plastic that won't rust</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">GOLD SIFTING PANS AND PIPETTES - Gold Panning kit has 2 dual riffle gold sifting pans; a 10” and an 8” diameter pan. These gold panning pans feature dual riffles and come in a deep color of your choice that will provide high contrast so you can identify gold flakes and gems easily. The included pipette droppers will assist with grabbing small flakes from the bottom of the pan easily</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">BLACK SAND MAGNET - Easily separate black sand from your gold pan with the prospectors 8lb magnet separator that works by squeezing the handle over magnetic particles to pick them out. There’s also a tweezer with a 4x magnifying glass so you can inspect your flakes and minerals more closely.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>ASR Outdoor 10pc Beginner Gold Panning Kit with 3oz Gold Paydirt Bag</h1>\n\t\t\t<p>The ASR Outdoor 10 piece gold panning kit comes with everything you’ll need to get started on your gold prospecting adventure. The tools included are designed to help you identify, clean, and collect the valuable gold flakes and minerals.</p><p>We've included a 3oz bag of gold pay dirt (total weight) from Professional Gold Prospector Bobby Bo's gold rich prospectors claim; in this you will find 20 to 30 mesh size&nbsp; fine to small gold designed for home practice and does not require any classification. It comes in a resealable bag for storage and safe keeping, great for all levels of gold prospectors.\n \nInside the kit, we’ve included a scoop digger which is an essential tool for your arsenal of gold prospecting and metal detecting equipment. It measures 12.5” in length with a beveled scoop edge so you can count on it to dig through dirt, sand, and silt in any weather.  It’s made of durable, high-quality ABS plastic that won't rust.\n \nThe kit also comes with 2 dual riffle gold sifting pans; a 10” and an 8” diameter pan. These pans feature deep and shallow riffles and provide high contrast so you can identify gold flakes and gems. The 2 included pipette droppers will assist with grabbing small flakes and washing them off for inspection. \n \n Additionally, we’ve added in a separator tool with an 8lb magnet to help you grab gold flakes and separate them from black sand while prospecting. There’s also a tweezer with a 4x magnifying glass so you can inspect your flakes and minerals more closely.\n \nLastly, we’ve added 3 glass collection vials so you can store your findings and keep them secured. Each glass vial has a capacity of 3mL (.75 drams) and comes with a water-tight plastic screw lid. \n \nThis essential gold panning kit is a great gift idea for yourself or other prospectors, whether they are beginners or experienced. Gold prospecting is also a fun activity for kids that encourages outdoor activity and exercise while learning about metal detecting.</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>© 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p></div></div><div style=\"clear:both\"><table></table>\n\t</div>\n\n <center><br></center>",
